page.title: 15CABOURNE HIGH,NEW CLOSE WOOD
page.content: There is a large variety of trees both coniferous eg scots pine, corsican pine, larch and broadleaved eg. oak,spanish chestnut, ash, sycamore, cherry, and beach. These are the main commercial tree species. The adult trees are usually felled when the trees annual growing rate decreases. The trees are made into different items:- {Larch}for boat building;they produce avery good quality of wood. {Pine}mainly furniture and doors. {Oak}for wood veneer perfect quality furniture,building,fencing,mining timbers. {Ash} furniture,tool handles,tent pegs,fencing rails. {Sycamore}furniture and veneer. Today tree felling is a highly profitable business and is the main source of income for the wooded areas.
